## Errors
- [ERR-02] **MUST** fail fast on programmer errors; return typed failures for recoverable cases.
- [ERR-03] **MUST** use standard API error shape: `{ code, message, details?, correlationId }`.

## Logging
- [LOG-01] **MUST** emit structured logs (JSON where supported) with correlation/trace IDs.
- [LOG-02] **MUST NOT** log secrets or PII; redact by default. (See `SEC-LOG-01`)

## Observability
- [OBS-01] **MUST** emit four golden signals: latency, traffic, errors, saturation.
- [OBS-02] **SHOULD** trace critical flows end-to-end; span names reflect domain actions.

## Exceptions
- [ADR-02] **MUST** record ADR if deviating from the standard error schema/log levels.
